    <h1>LeetCode 3454: Separate Squares II (C++)</h1>

    <div class="problem-description">
        <p><strong>Problem:</strong> You are given squares on a 2D plane. Find the horizontal line that divides the total area of squares into two equal halves.</p>
        <p><strong>Example:</strong> Input squares with different sizes and positions. Output the y-coordinate that splits their total area equally.</p>
    </div>

